parameters:
Brachiocondor: Gahaha... I'm glad you came, I really need
you! From the information flowing in, it seemed like you
were pretty down, so I was quite worried, but I'm relieved
to see you've bounced back!

Memimi: Hehe, thanks to Bunny-chan's message, I was able to
hold onto hope... As long as there's a chance to rebuild the
organization, I will stand up again and again.

Brachiocondor: (Seriously, she recovered well... If it were
me who got hit that hard, I'd be crying and hiding away.
Even if we take back the organization, it's not like the
videos and images are gone. What's she planning to do from
now on...)

Memimi: I've taken some social damage too, but I'm sure
things will work out somehow... You think so too, right
Brachiocondor...? Huh?

Bunny-chan: Memimi-chan, you've had it tough, huh~! Even
after seeing the message, I was worried you wouldn't come
here~! You did great, super great!

Memimi: Ugh, while I was feeling so down, your messages were
such an encouragement to my heart...! Thank you... Bunny-
chan, you're my best friend...!
Bunny-chan: Let's work hard together, Memimi-chan!

Shark Broccoli: Duke Shark, are you feeling alright? If
you're up for it, let's discuss what to do next...

Memimi: Of course I'm fine, Great Leader-sama... I won't
lose next time!

Memimi: My apologies, Great Leader-sama... My mental state
is still a bit unstable... Please give me a moment...

Shark Broccoli: Hmm, don't push yourself... Take your time
to rest. Let's postpone our discussion for a little while
longer...

Anomalocaris: Moss moss... I'm so glad to see you again! I
couldn't stand the thought of being done in by that orca
bastard! It's finally time to end my long period of hiding!

Memimi: Thank you for following my orders, Anomalocaris...
I'm proud to have a subordinate like you. If you had sided
with the mayor, you could have had a better life than
this...

Anomalocaris: (Now that I think about it, if I had betrayed
the organization, I could have made her do whatever I
wanted... like doing it raw or making her suck it...
gulp...)

Cerburus Octopus: All my revenue streams have been crushed,
and I'm feeling the pinch. Hurry up and revive the
organization so I can start earning again!

Memimi: Some of the shops that I entrusted to Cerburus
Octopus were also ruined by the mayor's interference. We'll
have to think about various financial strategies after the
organization's revival...

Cerburus Octopus: Once we take down the mayor, we should get
our hands on the revenue from the adult video streaming
site, so there's no need to worry about funds! It's trending
on social media, so by now it must be raking in an
astronomical amount, right?

Memimi: Personally, I don't really want to use that money...
I wonder if that streaming site is actually profitable, how
many subscribers it has... ugh...

Underling: I'm so glad Lord Shark has come to us!! I was
worried that in such a state, you wouldn't be able to make
it here and would have fled the town...

Memimi: Honestly, I thought this time might be the end for
me. If I had been hiding here, maybe no one would have seen,
but in town, I was subjected to quite a terrible ordeal...

Underling: I've been checking social media to grasp the
situation, so I'm almost fully aware of what Lord Shark has
been through! It must have been tough... having those
uncensored images spread all over the net... uh, haa haa...

Memimi: Please don't get excited while reminiscing... So I
was seen after all...

Underling: I knew you were in a tough situation, but it was
crucial that the organization's main monsters gathered here
didn't get exposed at any cost. I'm sorry I couldn't come to
your aid... Anomalocaris Mosman-sama was also conflicted.

Memimi: It's alright, not taking rash action to save me was
the right decision... After all, I can hardly say I'm
unharmed, but I made it here... There's no need to fret over
it.

Underling: About what happened in the underground city
earlier, I was secretly watching from the door. You were
even fed potatoes kneaded with someone's ass... It was so
exciting... I mean, it was so pitiful...

Memimi: You saw that-... That... That was really tough,
wasn't it... Ugh... Maybe I did want a little bit of help
after all...

Underling: Many of our comrades have been captured and
oppressed by the mayor, and some have even betrayed us. But
Cerberus Octopus-sama and I have stayed because we believe
in you and the boss...

Memimi: Thank you... Our organization is now less than a
tenth of what it once was, but let's figure out a way to
defeat him from here...

Underling: Right, as for us, it's one thing, but if you lose
again, I think you'll face a punishment far worse than an
AV... Let's be cautious...

Memimi: Stop... I try not to think about that... I've
decided never to be broken again, but still, I can't endure
going through that sort of thing again...
